        "subject": "LU-1548 ldiskfs: realign data in ldiskfs_inode_info for SLES11",
        "message": "LU-1548 ldiskfs: realign data in ldiskfs_inode_info for SLES11\n\nReposition a few items of ldiskfs_inode_info in ext4.h for the\nSLES11 SP1 kernel to remove the alignment hole in the structure,\ni.e. reduce the size of this structure, then each slab page can\nhold more objects(ldiskfs_inode_info).\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: If5b73e06cb747cf34e8bfa69cd0531b29a947b67\n"
